  "body": "- [ ] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\n\n---\n## Issue\n\nIf the contract contains the keyword pragma, compiling fails with:\n\n```\n/usr/local/lib/node_modules/truffle/node_modules/solidity-parser/index.js:39\n      throw e;\n      ^\nSyntaxError: Expected \"contract\", \"import\", \"library\", comment, end of input, end of line or whitespace but \"p\" found. Line: 1, Column: 1\n    at peg$buildException (/usr/local/lib/node_modules/truffle/node_modules/solidity-parser/build/imports_parser.js:423:14)\n    at Object.peg$parse [as parse] (/usr/local/lib/node_modules/truffle/node_modules/solidity-parser/build/imports_parser.js:3355:13)\n    at Object.parse (/usr/local/lib/node_modules/truffle/node_modules/solidity-parser/index.js:34:23)\n    at /usr/local/lib/node_modules/truffle/lib/profiler.js:134:36\n    at tryToString (fs.js:455:3)\n    at FSReqWrap.readFileAfterClose [as oncomplete] (fs.js:442:12)\n```\n## Steps to Reproduce\n\nUse a contract that starts with `pragma solidity 0.4.2;`\n## Expected Behavior\n\nit compiles\n## Actual Results\n\nit does not compile and throw an error\n## Environment\n- Operating System: OSX\n- Truffle version:v2.0.8\n- Ethereum client: n/a\n- node version: v6.6.0\n- npm version: 3.10.7\n",
